d:
The other Log Myu gallery was almost 100 pages behind, so I took it upon myself to keep it updated.

Despite accusations of nothing happening, I do like this production a lot. It's not the best "fuel", but it's very fun to see Myu slowly but surely succeed in becoming an absolute fatass. Also, an obligatory "be patient I have autism" for our favourite girl. Seems rather topical these days.
